	<h2 class="headline"><a href="http://boingboing.net/2012/07/28/poop-strong-young-cancer-pati.html" rel="bookmark">Poop Strong: Cancer patient whose costs exceeded insurance cap wins victory, via Twitter</a></h2>
	
	
	<p class="byline">
	
	By <span onmouseover="showAuthor('authorpopup-173740');" onmouseout="dontshowAuthor()"><a href="http://boingboing.net/author/xeni_jardin" title="Posts by Xeni Jardin" rel="author">Xeni Jardin</a></span> at 3:22 pm Saturday, Jul 28 
	
	&bull; <span><a href="http://boingboing.net/2012/07/28/poop-strong-young-cancer-pati.html#disqus_thread">Comments</a></span> &bull; <span onMouseOver="document.getElementById('sharethis-173740').style.display='inline'" id="sharethis-trigger-173740"><a href="javascript:void(0)">Share</a></span>
	
  		<span id="sharethis-173740" class="sharingbox">
	
		<span class="emailDiv">
			<a href="mailto:type%20email%20address%20here?subject=Shared%20from%20Boing Boing&body=Poop Strong: Cancer patient whose costs exceeded insurance cap wins victory, via Twitter - http://boingboing.net/2012/07/28/poop-strong-young-cancer-pati.html" title="Email to a friend/colleague" target="_blank">
