<div id="post-173673" class="post">

	<h2 class="headline"><a href="http://boingboing.net/2012/07/28/a-message-for-the-media-from-a.html" rel="bookmark">A message for the media from an Aurora shooting survivor: "Give victims and survivors their space"</a></h2>
	
	
	<p class="byline">
	
	By <span onmouseover="showAuthor('authorpopup-173673');" onmouseout="dontshowAuthor()"><a href="http://boingboing.net/author/xeni_jardin" title="Posts by Xeni Jardin" rel="author">Xeni Jardin</a></span> at 9:22 am Saturday, Jul 28 
	
